penai-responses","provider":"codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":1881,"output":794,"cacheRead":76800,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":79475,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774410392079}}
{"type":"message","id":"c94ab193","parentId":"599ddb38","timestamp":"2026-03-25T04:22:06.928Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-25 12:22:06 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | 张玲 (ou_968a615509dc191f04220e18cda67080) [msg:om_x100b5302601a50a4c3f07cc19a4e821]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5302601a50a4c3f07cc19a4e821\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_968a615509dc191f04220e18cda67080\",\n  \"sender\": \"张玲\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-03-25 12:22 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"张玲 (ou_968a615509dc191f04220e18cda67080)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_968a615509dc191f04220e18cda67080\",\n  \"name\": \"张玲\"\n}\n```\n\n为什么平衡和保守盘都给了信号买入，而进取盘还不买？这两个盘的风险偏好不应该更小吗？"}],"timestamp":1774412526925}}
