{"type":"message","id":"2d79af14","parentId":"6556fd0d","timestamp":"2026-03-25T13:47:29.357Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_tytOKRdh8htPXDQTlHXzY39f|fc_03f66048c5db434b0169c3e7704d8c819583aa5f35a51f9cde","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"generated_at\": \"2026-03-25 21:47:08\",\n  \"meeting_type\": \"night\",\n  \"date_tag\": \"20260325\",\n  \"dry_run\": true,\n  \"force\": false,\n  \"message\": \"🌙 模拟交易提示｜夜间研究会｜20260325\\n- 风险状态：偏防守\\n- 模拟买入观察：暂无\\n- 模拟卖出复核：当前策略未触发卖出/减仓复核。\\n- 执行门槛：需要人工确认\\n- 当前结论：只保留观察名单和触发条件，不自动转成买单。\\n- 当前非交易时段/非交易日，不提供可执行买价。\\n- 模拟盘快照：20260325 | 新鲜度=今日已刷新\\n- 模拟盘说明：三套模拟盘已刷新到今日 20260325。\\n- 数据源健康：非交易时段观察 | 推荐模式=halt_new_positions\\n- THS本地行情：已回退 | THS命中/回退/失败=0/3/0\\n- THS摘要：THS 本地实时行情出现回退，检测 3，THS 命中 0，回退 3\",\n  \"source_files\": {\n    \"trade_card\": \"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/investment_research_trade_card_night_20260325.json\",\n    \"chief_card\": \"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/investment_research_chief_card_night_20260325.json\",\n    \"control_tower_card\": \"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/investment_research_control_tower_card_20260325.json\",\n    \"control_tower\": \"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/investment_research_control_tower_20260325.json\",\n    \"chief_broadcast\": \"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/investment_research_chief_broadcast_night_20260325.md\",\n    \"group_digest\": \"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/investment_research_group_digest_night_20260325.md\",\n    \"publish_bundle\": \"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/investment_research_publish_bundle_night_20260325.json\"\n  },\n  \"health_snapshot\": {\n    \"scope\": \"overnight\",\n    \"path\": \"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/investment_research_data_source_health_overnight_20260325.json\",\n    \"status\": \"offhours_guarded\",\n    \"data_confidence\": \"low\",\n    \"confidence_score\": 31,\n    \"recommended_mode\": \"halt_new_positions\",\n    \"auto_actions\": [\n      \"非交易时段不提供可执行买价\",\n      \"仅输出观察池和人工确认后的触发条件\"\n    ],\n    \"breaches\": [],\n    \"observations\": [],\n    \"trading_time\": false,\n    \"max_price_diff_pct\": 4.3,\n    \"ths_market\": {\n      \"status\": \"fallback\",\n      \"available\": true,\n      \"checked\": 3,\n      \"ok_count\": 0,\n      \"fallback_count\": 3,\n      \"failed_count\": 0,\n      \"source_breakdown\": {\n        \"tushare\": 3\n      },\n      \"error\": \"\",\n      \"summary\": \"THS 本地实时行情出现回退，检测 3，THS 命中 0，回退 3\",\n      \"alert_text\": \"THS 本地实时行情已回退到非 THS 源，盘中信号需要人工复核。\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"deliveries\": [\n    {\n      \"target_name\": \"dm\",\n      \"channel\": \"feishu\",\n      \"account\": \"main\",\n      \"target\": \"user:ou_968a615509dc191f04220e18cda67080\",\n      \"status\": \"OK\",\n      \"dedupe_key\": \"559331f36933b636c3e7d03289ceb20d6bfd2b76f39da2e3234d4ce8cdb16326\",\n      \"info\": \"[plugins] feishu_chat: Registered feishu_chat, feishu_chat_members\\n[plugins] feishu_im: Registered feishu_im_user_message, feishu_im_user_fetch_resource, feishu_im_user_get_messages, feishu_im_user_get_thread_messages, feishu_im_user_search_messages\\n[plugins] feishu_drive: Registered feishu_drive_file, feishu_doc_comments, feishu_doc_media\\n[plugins] feishu_wiki: Registered feishu_wiki_space, feishu_wiki_space_node\\n[plugins] feishu_sheets: Registered feishu_sheet tool\\n[plugins] feishu_im_bot_image: Registered feishu_im_bot_image tool\\n[plugins] feishu_im: Registered feishu_im_bot_image\\n[plugins] Registered all OAPI tools (calendar, task, bitable, search, drive, wiki, sheets, im)\\n[plugins] feishu_oauth: Registered feishu_oauth tool\\n[plugins] feishu_oauth_batch_auth: Registered feishu_oauth_batch_auth tool\\n{\\n  \\\"action\\\": \\\"send\\\",\\n  \\\"channel\\\": \\\"feishu\\\",\\n  \\\"dryRun\\\": true,\\n  \\\"handledBy\\\": \\\"core\\\",\\n  \\\"payload\\