*没有伪装成“当日交易归因”**，而是先把摘要口径修正了。\n\n---\n\n### 修改文件\n- `scripts/push_investment_research_delivery.py`\n\n### 提交记录\n已提交 git：\n\n- `71ea2dc` — `fix delivery summary attribution for historical holdings`\n\n### 当前状态\n- `ACTIVE_TASK.md` 已收口为 `done`\n- workspace 相关文件已提交，当前这次修复是完整闭环\n\n如果你要，我下一步可以直接继续修第二层：\n\n**把这类“已有持仓但没退出规则”的票，真正接入卖出/减仓体系。**","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_03f66048c5db434b0169c3e83567d0819584d19695d4e8fa3e\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":258,"output":708,"cacheRead":131200,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":132166,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774446617815}}
