{"type":"message","id":"7af04e8e","parentId":"5b159f49","timestamp":"2026-03-25T14:01:36.147Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_V4ZkSzudgRCDkqdVt7rasBgo|fc_03f66048c5db434b0169c3eabd6de0819599e0e08e1d75486e","toolName":"memory_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"path\": \"memory/knowledge/20260305_112245_个人量化投资系统.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 1,\n      \"endLine\": 10,\n      \"score\": 0.47441420853137967,\n      \"snippet\": \"# 个人量化投资系统\\n\\n**日期**: 2026-03-05 11:22:45\\n**分类**: 知识库\\n**标签**: 无\\n\\n---\\n\\n正在开发中，使用Tushare获取数据，已下载654万条A股历史数据\\n\\nSource: memory/knowledge/20260305_112245_个人量化投资系统.md#L1-L10\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"citation\": \"memory/knowledge/20260305_112245_个人量化投资系统.md#L1-L10\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"path\": \"memory/archive/2026-03/2026-03-07.full.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 85,\n      \"endLine\": 112,\n      \"score\": 0.4438240766525268,\n      \"snippet\": \"- `quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/stock_alpha_v1_report_20260307.md`\\n  - `quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/stock_strategy_search_top30_20260307.json`\\n\\n## 09:16 个股实盘执行版v1落地（Durable）\\n- 用户确认“继续做直到实现目标”后，已继续推进并输出实盘执行版（非交易日口径）。\\n- 新增配置：`quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/config/live_stock_alpha_v3.json`。\\n- 新增执行报告：`quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/stock_alpha_live_execution_v1_20260307.md`。\\n- 口径：非交易日不输出可执行买价，仅给预算、仓位、开盘触发条件与风控阈值。\\n\\n## 09:20 DeepSeek问题复核与执行链路修正（Durable）\\n- 用户要求复核 DeepSeek 对策略的质疑并修正，核心关注“是否可实盘”。\\n- 已完成复核并形成报告：`quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/de\\n\\nSource: memory/archive/2026-03/2026-03-07.full.md#L85-L112\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"citation\": \"memory/archive/2026-03/2026-03-07.full.md#L85-L112\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"path\": \"memory/daily_progress_report.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 1,\n      \"endLine\": 26,\n      \"score\": 0.4193340510129928,\n      \"snippet\": \"# 量化系统项目进度汇报 - 2026-03-10 19:56\\n\\n## 今日提交\\n```\\n883201a feat: add candidate pool reporting and external risk config\\n1ffabe1 feat: apply risk engine to merged signals\\ncce0fb5 docs: add quant system optimization report for 2026-03-10\\nfef3bbc workspace: add execution discipline rules against fake progress\\n35d452e feat: add second strategy adapter and merged signal pipeline\\n```\\n\\n## 最新报告\\n- candidate_pool_report_20260310.md\\n\\n## 盘前检查状态\\n- 无状态\\n\\n## 当前阶段\\n（待填写：信号/风控/订单/报告链路进度）\\n\\n## 卡点\\n（待填写：如有阻断事项）\\n\\n---\\nGenerated by OpenClaw cron at 2026-03-10 19:56\\n\\nSource: memory/daily_progress_report.md#L1-L26\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"citation\": \"memory/daily_progress_report.md#L1-L26\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"path\": \"memory/archive/2026-03/2026-03-08-skill-evaluation.full.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 112,\n      \"endLine\": 172,\n      \"score\": 0.41071073114871975,\n      \"snippet\": \"- `flow` 动作用了未定义函数（`stock_individual_fund_flow`）\\n- 结论：**专业潜力最高，但现在不可直接生产用**\\n\\n3) **stock-daily-report**\\n- ❌ 当前直接失败：默认数据源抓不到行情（“所有数据源都无法获取”），报告无法生成\\n- 结论：**展示形式最专业，但当前数据抓取链路没打通**\\n\\n---\\n\\n### 排名（按“现在就能用且靠谱”）\\n- **可用性**：`stock-watcher` > `akshare-stock` > `stock-daily-report`\\n- **专业性上限**：`akshare-stock` > `stock-daily-report` > `stock-watcher`\\n- **综合结论**：目前没有一个达到“可直接信任用于交易决策”的标准。\\n\\n如果你同意，我下一步就做一轮“可生产修复”：\\n- 修 `akshare-stock` 的两个代码 bug\\n- 给 `stock-watcher` 改成结构化字段抓取（不再正则乱抓百分比）\\n- 给 `stock-daily-report` 加同花顺网页口径回退源  \\n然后我给你一版新的对比结论。\\nassistant: 我刚实测了你这几个 A 股 skill，结论很直接：\\n\\n### 实测结果\\n\\n1) **stock-watcher**\\n- ✅ 能跑通（添加/列出/抓行情都成功）\\n- ⚠️ 但“准确性一般”：它是从 10jqka 网页全文里用正则抓百分比，容易把无关百分比当成涨跌幅（我抓到过 `85%`、`10%` 这种明显异常值）\\n- 结论\\n\\nSource: memory/archive/2026-03/2026-03-08-skill-evaluation.full.md#L112-L172\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"citation\": \"memory/archive/2026-03/2026-03-08-skill-evaluation.full.md#L112-L172\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"path\": \"memory/archive/2026-03/2026-03-07.full.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 47,\n      \"endLine\": 71,\n      \"score\": 0.41080717444419856,\n      \"snippet\": \"## 07:41 A方案关键要素与归因说明（Durable）\\n- 已新增策略说明报告：`quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/strategy_A_key_elements_and_attribution_20260307.md`。\\n- 报告覆盖：因子体系（Alpha158+LGBM）、买卖逻辑（TopkDropout）、风控体系（宽度仓位+实盘阈值）、机制归因与风险提示。\\n\\n## 07:46 A方案聚宽回测脚本落地（Durable）\\n- 新增聚宽可运行版本：`quant_projects/quant_strategies/聚宽_A方案_宽度风控_T1.py`。\\n- 核心保留：TopkDropout参数（10/3/4）、宽度三档仓位（0.30/0.55/0.90）、T+1（使用`previous_date`打分）、风险阈值（单票/组合）。\\n- 成本口径按用户偏好：佣金 `0.000085`，卖出印花税 `0.001`，`min_commission=0`。\\n- 已完成本地语法检查：`python3 -m py_compile` 通过。\\n- 聚宽“无成交”原因与修复：默认资金下单笔金额过小（A股100股一手约束）导致无法成交；已新增最小手数约束与可承受仓位自动收缩逻辑，并将单票上限提升到20%。\\n- 二次修复（90万仍无成交）：进一步放宽阻断条件（指数熔断阈值由-1.5%改-3%）、缩小候选池避免`in_`过长导致取数失败、打分失败时启用fallback、连续5日无成交触发兜底开仓。\\n-\\n\\nSource: memory/archive/2026-03/2026-03-07.full.md#L47-L71\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"citation\": \"memory/archive/2026-03/2026-03-07.full.md#L47-L71\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"provider\": \"ollama\",\n  \"model\": \"bge-m3:latest\",\n  \"citations\": \"auto\",\n  \"mode\": \"hybrid\"\n}"}],"details":{"results":[{"path":"memory/knowledge/20260305_112245_个人量化投资系统.md","startLine":1,"endLine":10,"score":0.47441420853137967,"snippet":"# 个人量化投资系统\n\n**日期**: 2026-03-05 11:22:45\n**分类**: 知识库\n**标签**: 无\n\n---\n\n正在开发中，使用Tushare获取数据，已下载654万条A股历史数据\n\nSource: memory/knowledge/20260305_112245_个人量化投资系统.md#L1-L10","source":"memory","citation":"memory/knowledge/20260305_112245_个人量化投资系统.md#L1-L10"},{"path":"memory/archive/2026-03/2026-03-07.full.md","startLine":85,"endLine":112,"score":0.4438240766525268,"snippet":"- `quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/stock_alpha_v1_report_20260307.md`\n  - `quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/stock_strategy_search_top30_20260307.json`\n\n## 09:16 个股实盘执行版v1落地（Durable）\n- 用户确认“继续做直到实现目标”后，已继续推进并输出实盘执行版（非交易日口径）。\n- 新增配置：`quant